104
00:07:48,967 --> 00:07:51,407
Why didn't you tell me?

105
00:07:55,557 --> 00:07:58,147
You're both already so busy.

106
00:07:58,147 --> 00:08:00,487
I didn't want to worry you.

107
00:08:00,487 --> 00:08:03,847
