111
00:08:13,167 --> 00:08:15,317
Why the class transfer?

112
00:08:15,317 --> 00:08:18,647
You even lied by saying we knew about it.

113
00:08:18,647 --> 00:08:22,117
Actually, if that's his wish, so be it.

114
00:08:22,117 --> 00:08:24,847
He doesn't have to study abroad.

115
00:08:24,847 --> 00:08:27,920
Song Hang, stop trying to smooth things over.

116
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:31,677
The international class and studying abroad were all matters we discussed.

117
00:08:31,677 --> 00:08:35,197
