133
00:09:29,367 --> 00:09:33,377
I'm not highly educated, but I've been through hardships!

134
00:09:33,377 --> 00:09:39,167
Ever since you were born, I vowed never to let you suffer the same fate as me.

135
00:09:39,167 --> 00:09:43,597
Since you were little, I did all the research. I just wanted you to be

136
00:09:43,597 --> 00:09:48,927
- better than everyone else. 
 - I know. I know that, Mom. I understand.

137
00:09:48,927 --> 00:09:53,127
You've always put me first. I'm aware of that.

138
00:09:53,127 --> 00:09:55,037
Even when you...

139
00:09:55,797 --> 00:10:00,007
Walnuts are your favorite snack, but you gave them all to me, saying they were good for my brain.

140
00:10:00,007 --> 00:10:02,997
