148
00:10:25,087 --> 00:10:27,837
Fine, forget that I ever asked. Tell me now.

149
00:10:27,837 --> 00:10:31,917
What do you like? What don't you like? Tell me.

150
00:10:32,647 --> 00:10:34,837
