151
00:10:34,837 --> 00:10:37,237
I don't like walnuts.

152
00:10:46,927 --> 00:10:50,367
I want to be like everyone else.

153
00:10:50,367 --> 00:10:53,147
Sometimes, I really envy Xi Chi.

154
00:10:55,247 --> 00:10:58,597
I envy him when he jokes around with his friends.

155
00:10:58,597 --> 00:11:00,657
He can go home after school.

156
00:11:00,657 --> 00:11:03,057
He can join extracurricular activities.

157
00:11:03,057 --> 00:11:08,007
You and Dad may not believe me, but that's how I feel.

158
00:11:08,007 --> 00:11:11,577
My son, we...

159
00:11:11,577 --> 00:11:14,927
- We never knew you felt that wayâ€” 
 - Please, Mom and Dad.

160
00:11:14,927 --> 00:11:20,310
I didn't make this decision on a whim. I've already figured out what I want to study.

161
00:11:20,937 --> 00:11:23,297
What might that be?

162
00:11:23,297 --> 00:11:26,227
Tell me. What major is that?

163
00:11:30,077 --> 00:11:33,417
I'm giving you a chance. Why aren't you telling me?

164
00:11:36,437 --> 00:11:38,887
Fine, Song Cong.

165
00:11:38,887 --> 00:11:41,627
You are not being honest with us.

166
00:11:43,477 --> 00:11:46,717
I didn't believe it when they said raising a kid brings suffering.

167
00:11:46,717 --> 00:11:50,297
I never believed my son would be like that.

168
00:11:50,297 --> 00:11:52,877
But I know I'm wrong now.

169
00:11:55,897 --> 00:11:58,407
You don't like walnuts?

170
00:11:58,407 --> 00:12:01,147
Why didn't you tell me?

171
00:12:02,797 --> 00:12:04,817
I did everything for you.

172
00:12:04,817 --> 00:12:07,797
I did it all for your sake.

173
00:12:07,797 --> 00:12:11,037
- Have I not done everything for you? 
 - Mom!

174
00:12:11,887 --> 00:12:18,127
If you keep acting like this, how are you any different from Li Tian's mom?

175
00:12:20,027 --> 00:12:21,827
Song Cong!

176
00:12:34,247 --> 00:12:35,317
You want to quit?

177
00:12:35,317 --> 00:12:36,477
- Hao Mei! 
 - Fine.

178
00:12:36,477 --> 00:12:38,680
- Get rid of these. Save us some space. 
 - Mom!

179
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,837
- You don't need these! 
 - What is that for?

180
00:12:40,837 --> 00:12:41,987
- Calm down. 
 - Move aside!

181
00:12:41,987 --> 00:12:45,307
