183
00:13:05,537 --> 00:13:07,440
Did I hear that right?

184
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,840
Where are you going?

185
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:13,267
I said I'm joining the regular class.

186
00:13:13,267 --> 00:13:15,587
I told them about it.

187
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:21,297
Wait, have you lost your mind? Why would you want to be regular?

188
00:13:21,297 --> 00:13:24,527
