189
00:13:24,527 --> 00:13:28,287
I wanted to go to the Medical School at Yenching University.

190
00:13:28,287 --> 00:13:31,617
But if I told them that...

191
00:13:34,004 --> 00:13:36,124
It's best not to say it now.

192
00:13:37,027 --> 00:13:40,057
My goodness...

193
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:46,470
