194
00:13:49,597 --> 00:13:51,107
Wait.

195
00:13:51,107 --> 00:13:54,647
I think you must not tell them about the medical school.

196
00:13:54,647 --> 00:13:57,737
Your Mom always says she doesn't want you to have a tough life like your Dad,

197
00:13:57,737 --> 00:14:00,287
