198
00:14:00,287 --> 00:14:01,467
And the class transfer.

199
00:14:01,467 --> 00:14:02,657
Forget it.

200
00:14:02,657 --> 00:14:05,677
We all know how thrilled your mom was when you got the spot.

201
00:14:05,677 --> 00:14:08,177
Not just her, even I am worried about you.

202
00:14:08,177 --> 00:14:10,927
You asked me how I can be happy.

203
00:14:10,927 --> 00:14:13,497
The answer is to get transferred.

204
00:14:15,667 --> 00:14:19,287
I never thought your words could carry such weight.

205
00:14:19,287 --> 00:14:20,597
Impressive.

206
00:14:20,597 --> 00:14:21,747
Me?

207
00:14:21,747 --> 00:14:22,887
Who else?

208
00:14:22,887 --> 00:14:24,417
But...

209
00:14:27,437 --> 00:14:28,897
How about this?

210
00:14:28,897 --> 00:14:30,247
Be my witness.

211
00:14:30,247 --> 00:14:33,317
I tried talking him out of this, right?

212
00:14:33,317 --> 00:14:36,937
Fine. In that case, I welcome you to the

213
00:14:36,937 --> 00:14:40,200
"Not Supported by Parents but Still Staying True to Ourselves" Support Group.

214
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:43,197
We've waited for you for too long.

215
00:14:43,197 --> 00:14:44,677
Wait a second.

216
00:14:44,677 --> 00:14:48,657
Cong, are you really going against your own parents?

217
00:14:48,657 --> 00:14:49,717
Yeah.

218
00:14:49,717 --> 00:14:51,177
