219
00:14:51,177 --> 00:14:53,977
We can't let our parents decide for us.

220
00:14:54,957 --> 00:14:57,227
Xi Chi is right.

221
00:14:57,227 --> 00:15:00,827
Huan Er, you must have your own ambition.

222
00:15:01,437 --> 00:15:03,677
Me?

223
00:15:03,677 --> 00:15:08,177
I haven't even decided if I should be in the art or science stream.

224
00:15:15,717 --> 00:15:18,127
My dad asked me to have dinner at the noodle shop.

225
00:15:18,127 --> 00:15:20,807
We didn't get to eat anything just now.

226
00:15:21,407 --> 00:15:23,227
Aunt Hao must be fuming.

227
00:15:23,227 --> 00:15:25,347
She didn't make you dinner. Go on.

228
00:15:25,347 --> 00:15:26,947
See you around.

229
00:15:32,697 --> 00:15:36,407
A stalemate with parents can't go on forever.

230
00:15:36,407 --> 00:15:37,927
Indeed.

231
00:15:37,927 --> 00:15:40,027
We need a plan.

232
00:15:40,027 --> 00:15:41,767
But you saidâ€”

233
00:15:41,767 --> 00:15:46,017
He was so upset. I had to say things that would please him.

234
00:15:46,837 --> 00:15:48,647
You have a point.

235
00:15:48,647 --> 00:15:52,467
If the stalemate worsens, he'll never get transferred.

236
00:15:52,467 --> 00:15:56,467
We need to find a way to smooth things over.

237
00:16:00,167 --> 00:16:05,127
Since Aunt Hao is impossible to convince, we can take a detour.

238
00:16:05,127 --> 00:16:06,927
I'll try my luck with Uncle Song.

239
00:16:06,927 --> 00:16:08,507
Talk to Cong when you have time.

240
00:16:08,507 --> 00:16:10,127
Me? It won't work.

241
00:16:10,127 --> 00:16:12,887
You must try. You're the cause of this mess.

242
00:16:12,887 --> 00:16:14,247
Me?

243
00:16:14,247 --> 00:16:15,437
You heard him.

244
00:16:15,437 --> 00:16:19,277
You somehow inspired him. A random comment ended up changing everything.

245
00:16:20,557 --> 00:16:22,887
Therefore, Comrade Huan Er,

246
00:16:22,887 --> 00:16:26,527
you must complete the mission of assisting Comrade Song Cong.

247
00:16:26,527 --> 00:16:28,137
Thank you.

248
00:16:30,127 --> 00:16:33,627
The family will fall apart without me.

249
00:16:36,887 --> 00:16:37,797
What do I do...

